### Radius

| Token | Value | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `--radius-none` | 0 | No rounding — tables, full-bleed images |
| `--radius-sm` | <!-- PARAMETERIZE: radius_sm --> | Chips, badges, small tags |
| `--radius-md` | <!-- PARAMETERIZE: radius_md --> | Buttons, inputs, small cards (default) |
| `--radius-lg` | <!-- PARAMETERIZE: radius_lg --> | Cards, modals, larger surfaces |
| `--radius-xl` | <!-- PARAMETERIZE: radius_xl --> | Feature hero cards, large panels |
| `--radius-full` | 9999px | Pills, avatar circles |

