### Shadows

| Token | Use |
|---|---|
| `--shadow-none` | No shadow — flat surfaces, tables |
| `--shadow-xs` | Hairline lift — inputs, chips |
| `--shadow-sm` | Cards at rest |
| `--shadow-md` | Cards on hover, dropdowns |
| `--shadow-lg` | Modals, drawers, toasts |
| `--shadow-xl` | Full-screen overlays |

